<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>GitHub Test Page</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f7f6;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .container {
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 100%;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #24292e; /* Màu đặc trưng của GitHub */
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        p {
            color: #586069;
            font-size: 1.1em;
        }
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #2cbe4e;
            color: white;
            padding: 5px 15px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>Hello GitHub!</h1>
        <p>Đoạn code HTML này đang hoạt động hoàn toàn bình thường.</p>
        <div class="status-badge">Test Success</div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
